Tyrone Power Sr https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tyrone_Power_Sr 0 Frederick Tyrone Edmond Power Jr. (2 May 1869 – 23 December 1931) was an English-born American stage and screen actor, known professionally as Tyrone Power. He is now usually referred to as Tyrone Power Sr. to differentiate him from his son, actor Tyrone Power.
